{
  "chapter": "071",
  "title": "樗里子甘茂列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "樗里子出身称智囊",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>名叫疾，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦惠王</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠王</span>异<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>。他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>子。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>滑稽而多智谋，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国人称他为\"智囊\"。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "立功受封为严君",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦惠王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">八年</span>，封<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">右更</span>，派他率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲沃</span>，将城中居民全部驱逐，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">夺取</span>其城，土地归入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦惠王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十五年</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>为将<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄豹</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蔺</span>邑。第<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，辅助<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏章</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将领</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">屈丐</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">夺取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>之地。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>赏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>，号为严<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "拜相用事历三王",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦惠王</span>去世，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>即位，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">驱逐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏章</span>，任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>为左右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>。 派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>带<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百乘</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>国。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>派士卒迎接他，态度甚为恭敬。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王听说后发怒，责备<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>国，因其厚待<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国来客。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">游腾</span>替<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>国游说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">知伯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">仇犹</span>时，送给它一辆大<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，随后带兵跟进，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">仇犹</span>国于是灭亡。为什么？因为没有防备。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐桓公</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>国，名义上说是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，实际上是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭</span>击<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国是<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎狼</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">之国</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>带<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百乘</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">仇犹</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>国为鉴，所以派长<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">戟</span>在前，强<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弩</span>在后，名义上是保卫樗里疾，实际上是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span>禁他。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>国难道能不为其<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span>担忧吗？恐怕<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一旦</span>国家灭亡而令大王忧虑。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王于是高兴起来。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "昭王立樗里子益重",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦武王</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>即位，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>更加尊贵受重。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "解围蒲城显智略",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>邑。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>城守将害怕，请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡衍</span>求援。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡衍</span>替<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>说：\"您<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>，是为了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国呢，还是为了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国呢？为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国就好了，为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国就不划算了。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>国之所以能成为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>国，就是因为有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>邑。现在<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>并入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>必定折服于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国失去<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>之外还没法收复，是因为兵力弱。现在把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>并入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国必定强大。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国强盛之日，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>之外必定危殆了。况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王要观察您的行事，若损害<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>而有利于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，王必定<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">怪罪您。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>说：\"怎么办？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡衍</span>说：\"您放弃<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>邑不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>试为您进入城中说此事，以此让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>感激您。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>说：\"好。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡衍</span>进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>邑，对守将说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>知道<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>的困境了，他说一定要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>邑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">衍</span>能让他放弃<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>邑不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>。\" <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>守恐惧，于是再拜道：\"愿如此请求。\" 于是献<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>〖$三百斤</span>，说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵若退，请一定向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>推荐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>南面为侯。\" 所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡衍</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>邑受了<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>，又从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>国得了尊贵身份。 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>解围<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲</span>邑而离去。 返回时<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">皮氏</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">皮氏</span>未<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span>，又离去。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "卒而预言宫夹墓",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>去世，葬于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭南</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">章台</span>之东。他生前说：\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百年（时长）</span>之后，这里应当有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的宫殿夹着我的墓。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>的宅第在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>庙西<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭南</span>阴乡的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里</span>，所以世俗称他为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>。到了汉朝兴起，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长乐宫</span>在他墓的东面，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">未央宫</span>在他墓的西面，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武库</span>正对着他的墓。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>人谚语说：\"力气数<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任鄙</span>，智谋数<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里</span>。\""
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "甘茂入秦佐平蜀",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>是下<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>人。曾师从下<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">史举</span>先生，学习<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">百家</span>之术。通过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>求见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦惠王</span>。秦王见了他很喜欢，派他为将，辅佐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏章</span>略<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>地。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "甘茂入秦佐平蜀",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠王</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏章</span>离去，向东投奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>侯<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">煇</span>与相<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">壮</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">叛</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>前去平<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>国。归来后，任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>为左<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>为右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "息壤设盟拔宜阳",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦武王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>想让<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>马通行<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三川</span>，以窥视<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>室，那么<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>死也不朽了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>说：\"请允许<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国，约定共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国，请派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>辅佐我同往。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国后，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>回去，对王说'<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国听从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>了，但希望王不要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span>'。事情成功，全都算做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>的功劳。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>回国，把此话告知王，王到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">息壤</span>迎接<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>到后，王问他缘故。他回答道：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>是大县，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>积蓄已久。名义上叫县，实际上是郡。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>背负多重险阻，行军<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>它，很难。从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾参</span>住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">费</span>邑，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国有一个与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾参</span>同姓名的人<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了人，有人告诉他<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲说'<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾参</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>人了'，他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲照旧织布如故。过了一会儿，又一人告诉她说'<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾参</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>人了'，他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲仍照旧织布如故。又过一会儿，再一人告诉她说'<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾参</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>人了'，他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲扔下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">杼</span>，跳下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">机</span>，翻墙而逃。以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾参</span>的贤德和他<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲对他的信任，三个人怀疑他，他<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲也害怕起来。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的贤德不如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾参</span>，王信任<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>又不如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾参</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲信任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">参</span>，怀疑<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的不止三人，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>担心大王也会扔下<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">杼</span>啊。当初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>西面兼并<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">巴蜀</span>之地，北面开拓<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>之外，南面<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>得<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上庸</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>人并不归功于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张子</span>而把贤名归于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏文侯</span>命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐羊</span>为将<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>国，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>才<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取之。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐羊</span>回国论功，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文侯</span>给他看一箱诽谤他的<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">书信。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐羊</span>拜首再三说：'这不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的功劳，是主<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的力量啊。'如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>是羁旅之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙奭</span>两人会依附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国来非议此事，王一定会听信，这样王就欺骗了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>王，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>就会受<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲侈</span>的怨恨。\" 王说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>不会听的，请与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>盟誓。\" 最终派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五月</span>不能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻拔</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙奭</span>果然争辩此事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>回来，想罢兵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">息壤</span>的盟誓在那里呢。\" 王说：\"确有其事。\" 于是大举起兵，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span>。<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>首〖$六万</span>，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩襄王</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲侈</span>入秦谢罪，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>讲和。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "救韩雍氏立大功",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>终于到了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>都，并死于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>。他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟即位，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>。昭王<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣太后</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>子。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚怀王</span>怨恨先前<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丹阳</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国不来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span>援，于是派兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍氏</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲侈</span>向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>告急。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>刚刚即位，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>又是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人，不肯<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span>援。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>借重<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">茂</span>替<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>正期盼<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>〖◈救援，所以敢于抵御<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国。现在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍氏</span>被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军不出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">殽</span>山，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>就会高抬着头不来朝见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公叔</span>就会带韩国南向联合<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>联合为一，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>氏不敢不听从，这样<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国的形势就形成了。不知是坐等别国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span>好，还是主动<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span>别人好？\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王说：\"好。\" 于是发兵出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">殽</span>山来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">救</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>兵退去。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "政争失势亡奔齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>平<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>之乱，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">皮氏</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣太后</span>的外<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">戚</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>从小一起长大，因此被任用。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国器重<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>，就厚礼款待他。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>替<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>，准备<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>说：\"被擒之禽因困境可掀翻<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>子。您<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国，侮辱了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>收拾国家再次侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，自认为必定可以受<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>。现在您和<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国把解口之地让给它，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>小<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杜阳</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>楚联合，再<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>〖◆韩</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国必定灭亡。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国亡后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>就会亲自率领他的私属来阻遏<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。望公仔细考虑。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>说：\"我联合<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>楚并不是为了针对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>替<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">寿</span>转告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span>，说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>之交可以联合。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>答道：\"我希望对您进言。人们说'看重别人之所以看重的东西的人才会被看重'。王喜爱并亲近您，不如亲近<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙奭</span>；王看重您的智能，不如看重<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>。如今这两人都无法亲近<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国事务，而您独自与王主断国政，为什么呢？就是因为他们有过失。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙奭</span>偏向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>偏向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国，所以王不信任他们。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>争强，而您偏向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，这与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙奭</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>走的是同一条路，您有什么不同？人人都说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国善变，而您必因此而亡，这是自找责难。您不如和王谋划楚国善变的应对之策，亲善<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国来防备<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，这样就无忧患了。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">韩氏</span>必先以国家从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙奭</span>，后把国家托付给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国是您的仇敌。现在您说亲善<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国来防备<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，这是对外举事不回避仇敌。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>说：\"是的，我很想联合<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国。\" 答：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>答应给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公仲</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武遂</span>，归还<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>，现在您一人收手此事，恐怕很难。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>说：\"那怎么办？<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武遂</span>终究得不到了吗？\" 答：\"您何不通过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国替<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国索取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍川</span>？这是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国寄放的土地。您去索要而得到，这是号令通行于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国而以土地让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国感恩。您索要而未得到，这是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之间的怨恨不解而共同投奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>争强，您缓缓挑拨<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国以收服<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国，这对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国有利。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>说：\"怎么办？\" 答：\"这是一件好事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>想用<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙奭</span>想用<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。现在您<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>作为功劳，收服<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>使之安定，再<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>责<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的罪状，这样就能让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙奭</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>失去权势了。\""
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "辗转齐楚终客死",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>终于向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span>进言，将<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武遂</span>归还<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙奭</span>据理力争，没能争成。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙奭</span>因此怨恨，〖[谗害<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">茂</span>恐惧，中止<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒲阪</span>，逃离秦国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>讲和，停战。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "甘茂亡秦见苏代",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>逃离<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国投奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国时，路遇<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">代</span>替<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>得罪<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，害怕而逃亡，无处容身。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说穷人家<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>子和富人家<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>子一起绩麻，穷人家<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>子说：'我没钱买<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">烛</span>，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">烛</span>光幸而有余，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>可以分给我剩余的光，对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>的光明毫无损失而我却方便了。'如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>困窘而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>正好出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国当权用事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">茂</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻子</span>都在那里，愿<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>以余光救济他们。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>答应了。 于是到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国履行使命。 完成后，顺便劝说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>不是寻常的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人。他在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国时，累世受重。自<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">殽塞</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鬼谷</span>，那里的地形险易他都熟知。他要以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>联合<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>过来〖[图谋<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，这对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国不利。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王说：\"那怎么办？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>说：\"王不如重其聘礼，厚其俸禄，迎他回来，他若来就把他安置在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鬼谷</span>，终身不许他出来。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王说：\"好。\" 当即赐他<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上卿</span>爵位，派使者带相<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国迎接他。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>不去。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>是个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤人</span>。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国赐他<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上卿</span>爵位，用相<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>去迎他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>感念王的恩赐，乐意做王的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>下，所以推辞不去。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>打算以何等礼仪对待他？\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王说：\"好。\" 当即封他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上卿</span>，留他在齐。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国也因此恢复<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>的家业以讨好<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "楚相争议不入秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚怀王</span>刚与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国结为姻亲关系，正在高兴。 但<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，派人对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王说：\"希望把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>送回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蜎</span>：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>想在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国设置相国，谁可以？\" 答：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>不足以识别。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>王说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>想让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>为相，可以吗？\" 答：\"不可以。那<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">史举</span>，是下<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">监门，大不能事奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主，小不能治家，以苟且卑贱不廉洁闻名于世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>事奉他却顺从无间。所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠王</span>的明智，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>的明察，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张仪</span>的善辩，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>事奉他们，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>得〖$十</span>个官职而没有罪过。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">茂</span>确实是个贤能之人，但不可以让他在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国为相。因为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国有贤相，不是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的利益。况且王先前曾任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召滑</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国，内部施行章义之难，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国大乱，所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国南面〖[塞住厉门而建<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江东</span>为郡。算算王的功业之所以能如此，是因为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国乱而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国治。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>知道用在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国却忘了用在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>认为王的过错太大了。那么王如果想在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国设置相国，最好是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王亲近，小时候与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王同<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>而穿，长大后同<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>而乘，秦王听他理事。王一定要<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>为相，这对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国有利。\" 于是派使者向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>请求以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>为相。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国最终任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>为相。 而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>终究未能再入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，死于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "甘茂有孙曰甘罗",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>有一个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "甘罗事吕不韦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>死后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>年方十二岁，事奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>相<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "甘罗说张唐相燕",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦始皇</span>帝派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刚成君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡泽</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>后<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王喜</span>派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国当人质。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张唐</span>前去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国为相，想要与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国来扩展<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河间</span>之地。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张唐</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>曾经替<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国怨恨<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，说：'抓到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">唐</span>者赏<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>之地。'现在到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国必经<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>不能前往。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span>不高兴，还未能强令他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>侯为何如此不快？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span>说：\"我让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刚成君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡泽</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国效力<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹</span>已经来做人质了，我亲自请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张卿</span>去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>为相，他不肯去。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>请求去劝他。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span>呵斥道：\"滚开！我亲自请他都不肯去，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>小子能说服他吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>说：\"大<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项橐</span>七岁时就做了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>的老师。现在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>已生下十二岁了，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>可以试试<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，为何就这样呵斥呢？\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张卿</span>说：\"您的功劳与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武安君</span>相比如何？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卿</span>答道：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武安君</span>南面<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">挫败强大的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，北面威震<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>胜<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>城邑〖[堕毁无数，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的功劳比不上他。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">应侯</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国掌权时，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span>的专权相比，哪个更甚？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张卿</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">应侯</span>不如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span>专权。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>说：\"卿明明知道自己不如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span>专权？\" 答：\"知道。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">应侯</span>想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武安君</span>为难他，结果刚离<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>〖$七里</span>就在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杜邮</span>立被赐死。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span>亲自请卿到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>为相而卿不肯去，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>不知卿将死在何处了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张唐</span>说：\"那就请因孺<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>您的话而前往。\" 于是命人整理行装。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "甘罗使赵得五城",
      "text": "出发的日子已定，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span>说：\"借给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五乘</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，请容我为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张唐</span>先到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国通报。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文信侯</span>于是进宫对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span>说：\"从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>，年纪虽小，但他是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">名家</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都听说过他。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张唐</span>想称病不去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国为相，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>说服他去了。现在请让他先去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国通报，请允许派遣他。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">始皇</span>召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵悼襄王\">赵襄王（赵悼襄王）</span>到郊外迎接<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王说：\"王听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹</span>入质于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>了吗？\" 答：\"听说了。\" 又问：\"听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张唐</span>要去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>为相了吗？\" 答：\"听说了。\" \"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹</span>入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，表明<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国不欺骗<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张唐</span>去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国为相，表明<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国不欺骗<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>互不欺骗，若<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，赵国就危险了。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>互不欺骗没有别的缘故，就是想要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>而扩展<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河间</span>之地。王不如赐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五城</span>以扩展<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河间</span>，请允许<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>回去让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>归还<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，然后与强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>弱<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王当即割<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五城</span>以扩展<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河间</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国归还<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，得<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上谷</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十城</span>，让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国分到<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十一</span>座。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "甘罗封上卿",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>回去报告<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上卿</span>，又把当初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>的田宅赐予他。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樗里子</span>因是骨肉至亲而受重，本是情理之中的事，而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国人称道他的智慧，所以颇多采录其事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>起于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">下蔡</span>闾巷，显名于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之间，让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>更加强大。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>年纪虽小，却能出一奇计，声名传于后世。他虽非行为笃实的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君子</span>，但也是<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：历史时期\">战国（历史时期）</span>的策<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国强盛之时，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>人尤其喜好谋诈之术啊。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "严<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>名疾，他的称号是\"智囊\"。 既亲近又受重用，称兵于外国。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘茂</span>一同为相，起初辅佐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏章</span>。 起初推荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">向寿</span>，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>取<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宜阳</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘罗</span>年方妙龄，却能启用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张唐</span>。"
    }
  }
}